            <thetext>There is no possibility to align the text (or the icon/checkbox) of the checkbox widget. It would be usefull for multiline text, if you could align the text or the icon to the top or button.

This is how it is now: (see screenshot, # -&gt; checkbox)

   texttexttexttexttexttexttexttext
# texttexttexttexttexttexttexttext
   texttexttexttexttexttexttexttext

It would be nice to do something like this:

# texttexttexttexttexttexttexttext
   texttexttexttexttexttexttexttext
   texttexttexttexttexttexttexttext</thetext>
